<view class="weui-title">
      <text>填写表格</text>
    </view>
<view class='history-table-wrap'>
    <view class="table">
      <view class="tr">
          <view class="th th0">类别</view>
          <view class="th th1">评分内容</view>
          <view class="th th2">判断</view>
          <view class="th th3">分值</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tr" >
          <view class="td td0 tds1">主要标准</view>
          <view class="td td1">炎性关节病(关节、脊柱、肌腱)</view>
          <view class="td td2">
            <picker class='picker' bindchange="bindPickerSelect1" value="{{select1}}" range="{{arrSelect1}}">
          <view>{{arrSelect1[select1]}}
            <image class='image1' mode='aspectFit' src="/pages/image/xlk.png"></image>
          </view>
        </picker>
          </view>
          <view class="td td3">{{part1}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tr" >
          <view class="td td0"></view>
          <view class="td td1">1. 现发银屑病、银屑病既往史或家族史的证据（现发银屑病赋值2分，其他表现则赋值1分）*。</view>
          <view class="td td2">
            <picker class='picker' bindchange="bindPickerSelect2" value="{{select2}}" range="{{arrSelect2}}">
          <view>{{arrSelect2[select2]}}
            <image class='image1' mode='aspectFit' src="/pages/image/xlk.png"></image>
          </view>
        </picker>
          </view>
          <view class="td td3">{{part2}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tr" >
      <view class="td td0"></view>
          <view class="td td1">2. 就诊时可见典型的银屑病指甲改变，包括甲剥离、顶针样改变、过度角化等表现。</view>
          <view class="td td2">
              <picker class='picker' bindchange="bindPickerSelect3" value="{{select3}}" range="{{arrSelect3}}">
          <view>{{arrSelect3[select3]}}
            <image class='image1' mode='aspectFit' src="/pages/image/xlk.png"></image>
          </view>
        </picker>
          </view>
          <view class="td td3">{{part3}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tr" >
      <view class="td td0">次要标准</view>
          <view class="td td1">3. 类风湿因子检查结果为阴性。（类风湿因子可用除凝胶法外的其他方法检测，但最好采用酶联免疫吸附试验或比浊法，按当地实验室检查的参考值范围）</view>
          <view class="td td2">
              <picker class='picker' bindchange="bindPickerSelect4" value="{{select4}}" range="{{arrSelect4}}">
          <view>{{arrSelect4[select4]}}
            <image class='image1' mode='aspectFit' src="/pages/image/xlk.png"></image>
          </view>
        </picker>
          </view>
          <view class="td td3">{{part4}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tr" >
      <view class="td td0"></view>
          <view class="td td1">4. 具有整个指趾肿胀的指趾炎表现，或由风湿病医师记录的指趾炎病史。</view>
          <view class="td td2">
              <picker class='picker' bindchange="bindPickerSelect5" value="{{select5}}" range="{{arrSelect5}}">
          <view>{{arrSelect5[select5]}}
            <image class='image1' mode='aspectFit' src="/pages/image/xlk.png"></image>
          </view>
        </picker>
          </view>
          <view class="td td3">{{part5}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tr" >
      <view class="td td0"></view>
          <view class="td td1">5. 影像学证据显示关节周围新骨形成，表现为手足平片可见关节周围异常骨化(而非骨赘形成)。 </view>
          <view class="td td2">
              <picker class='picker' bindchange="bindPickerSelect6" value="{{select6}}" range="{{arrSelect6}}">
          <view>{{arrSelect6[select6]}}
            <image class='image1' mode='aspectFit' src="/pages/image/xlk.png"></image>
          </view>
        </picker>
          </view>
          <view class="td td3">{{part6}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tr" >
      <view class="td td0 tds2">诊断标准
      
      </view>
          <view class="td td1">主要标准伴有次要标准3分或3分以上者，即符合CASPAR分类标准。</view>
          <view class="td td2">
              <picker class='picker' bindchange="bindPickerSelect7" value="{{select7}}" range="{{arrSelect7}}">
          <view>{{arrSelect7[select7]}}
            <image class='image1' mode='aspectFit' src="/pages/image/xlk.png"></image>
          </view>
        </picker>
          </view>
          <view class="td td3"><input type='text'></input></view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='keep'>
    <button class='weui-btn' bindtap='keep'>保存</button>
 </view>
 </view>
 
